HEADWORD: birthrate
<hw>birthrate</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the ratio
of live births in an area to the population of that area; usually
expressed as births per 1000 population per year.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fertility, fertility rate.</syn>⟦br⟧
